Name: Falcon 9 Block 5 | Axiom Space Mission 4
Pad: Launch Complex 39A (Kennedy Space Center, FL, USA)
Mission: This is a Crew Dragon flight for a private company Axiom Space. The mission will carry a professionally trained commander alongside three private astronauts to and from the International Space Station. This crew will stay aboard space station for  at least eight days.
